description: This green machine is meandering through Orange County, pleasing local foodies with their authentic and flavorful Mediterranean street cuisine, with a side of sweet, attentive service. Your picks include Middle Eastern favorites like Falafel and Shawarma. You can pile it all on a pita or a plate, either way, it’s all completely kosher and crazy delicious. For the most scrumptious treats of the Middle East, come out and enjoy The Middle Eats!
name: The Middle Eats
